snippet.title: NecroVisioN Official Game Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
1C has just revealed their official trailer for the upcoming horror FPS NecroVisioN, the game that sees gamers crawling through the trenches of World War I and straight into the jaws of Hell.  Check out http://nixiepixel.com/blog/index.php/necrovision-pc-game for more info and exclusive screenshots! 

What do you guys think?  Remind anyone of  "You are Empty?"

( Video uploaded with permission of 1C Company.) Fight for the users in our Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/CKYwgxA
